Requirements
- Linux kernel 3.16 or later
- alsa-lib
- autoconf
- automake
- glib-2.0
- gobject-2.0

How to build
 $ ./autogen.sh
 $ ./configure
 $ make
 $ make install

How to test
(needless to install)
 $ ./autogen.sh
 $ ./configure
 $ make
 $ ./test/run.sh [gtk|qt4|qt5]
gtk - PyGObject is required.
qt4 - PyQt4 is resuired (python2 only).
qt5 - PyQt5 is required.

Overview
see 'doc/overview.png'.
